{
  "stem": "1917.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was a communist all my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I worked with the Romanian underground to help bring communism to Romania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But he said, it doesn't work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Once they got into power, every single one of them was trying to make money for himself without worrying about the ideals of what we worked for.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He said, he was running a pharmacy for the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "All the profits were going to the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he said he  was going to expose the people who were pocketing the money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And in order to shut him up, they put him in jail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The only reason they let him out is to leave Romania.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, children, it's my opinion that if you don't [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] believe in communism, or you don't want communism when you are 16, you don't have a heart.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if you still want communism when you are 26, you don't have a brain, because he said, the ideals of it are beautiful.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it just doesn't work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- ship-- I think were on the ocean-- I don't know-- five days maybe-- three days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never saw the-- the cabins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were always on the top of the deck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That ship was meant for 1,000.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was loaded with 3,000 immigrants-- all survivors of camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And lucky for us, because after our ship, they closed down the-- the gates or Romania for two years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The ship pulled up in Haifa early morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think on purpose it was designed that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People started singing the 'Hatikvah.' And the sun-- if you've ever been to Haifa, Mt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Carmel is there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the sun in June, it's always sunny.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The sun was rising.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the rays were high above.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
